This is how to minSubArraySum of nums:
  Remember that best is item 0 in nums
  Remember that current is item 0 in nums
  Remember that i is 1
  Do this nums's length times:
    When i is at most diff of nums's length and 1, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    Remember that current is min of item i in nums and sum of current and item i in nums
    Remember that best is min of best and current
    Increase i
  End do
  The answer is best
